<div class="content" name="DFS_INFO_1" uuid="c76762de-1249-485e-8a30-b1ff37179a3d"><p>The DFS_INFO_1 structure contains the name of a <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_639b7503-b879-4ef7-98a8-14adf85bc16d" data-linktype="relative-path">DFS root</a> or <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_0611e93d-f0e7-42ee-a591-d77ebcbb6619" data-linktype="relative-path">DFS link</a>. </p><p>The DFS_INFO_1 structure has the following format.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct _DFS_INFO_1 {
   [string] WCHAR* EntryPath;
 } DFS_INFO_1;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>EntryPath:</b>  The pointer to a DFS
root or a DFS link path.</p></div>